stolen gem<br>
-------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
<br>
As many of you may know, I have warming my blade upon the aviaks of South Karana for a few days. In truth, I am embarassed to admit this..but...I was carefully sharpening the ceremonial dagger that we might have a clean cut for our new dread harvesters, when a black cloud seemed to cover the sky. Swift as lightning an Aviak dropped down and tried to wrench the dagger from my hand. I reacted quickly and stabbed at the bird, but he quickly evaded my action.<br>
<br>
Now I wreak my revenge on all the Aviaks, looking for something....Though I saved the dagger from certain loss, the Aviak plucked a gem from its hilt, and flew swiftly away. Oh, that I had the power to levitate, I might have overtaken him.<br>
<br>
If any among you wish to be part of this quest and kill aviaks, I will look at the gems you recover and try to find the one we are missing. I offer a reward of 50p to any who are able to recover the missing stone.<br>
<br>
Hate with honor<br>
Creapiing V'Etch<br>
