My blade bloody from battling the Aviaks, a messenger approached me timidly, bowed, and departed. Creapiing quickly scanned the message. We have joined in the hunt for the gem, Reaper--We have vowed to recover it. She briefly medidtated,knowing that in the last 4 days in which she had bloodied all of south Karana seeking the gem, how carefully hidden it must be. If I must bring in all of the Violent Harvest, she vowed, we WILL recover the gem. I myself will raze the entire Aviak Tree If I must.<br>
<br>
She turned, puzzled to see the messenger still there, then noted the second message in his hand. She nodded, took the message, and dismissed the messenger. Sigh! She would have to waylay her slaughtering of the birds for a brief time to attend to other matters, but she would return very soon to continue the hunt.<br>
<br>
